FATAL FUN WITH DICK AND JANE 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By E.J. MONTINI 
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   See Dick.
</P>
<P>
   See Jane.
</P>
<P>
   See Father. Father is armed.
</P>
<P>
   Look, Dick. Look, Jane.
</P>
<P>
   Father holds a gun. Gun is silver. Gun is heavy. Gun shines.
</P>
<P>
   Father smiles.
</P>
<P>
   Dick sees.
</P>
<P>
   Jane sees.
</P>
<P>
   Spot sees.
</P>
<P>
   ``Bowwow,'' says Spot.
</P>
<P>
   ``Ssssssh,'' says Dick.
</P>
<P>
   ``Ssssssh,'' says Jane.
</P>
<P>
   See father's desk. See drawer. See father put gun in drawer.
</P>
<P>
   Dick smiles.
</P>
<P>
   Jane smiles.
</P>
<P>
   ``Bowwow,'' says Spot.
</P>
<P>
   Father looks.
</P>
<P>
   ``Come, Spot,'' says Father.
</P>
<P>
   Spot goes.
</P>
<P>
   See bullets.
</P>
<P>
   Bullets are small.
</P>
<P>
   Bullets are shiny.
</P>
<P>
   See father's dresser. See sock drawer. See Father put bullets
under socks.
</P>
<P>
   Look, Dick.
</P>
<P>
   Look, Jane.
</P>
<P>
   Look, no trigger lock. Look, no gun safety. Look, no license.
Look, no registration. Look, no training. Look, no common sense.
</P>
<P>
   Father goes.
</P>
<P>
   Where is Father?
</P>
<P>
   Where is Mother?
</P>
<P>
   Is Mother working? Is Mother asleep? Is Mother as dumb as
Father?
</P>
<P>
   See Dick.
</P>
<P>
   See Dick get gun.
</P>
<P>
   See Jane.
</P>
<P>
   See Jane get bullets.
</P>
<P>
   Next comes loading. Loading is fun. Click. Click. Click.
</P>
<P>
   Dick laughs.
</P>
<P>
   Jane laughs.
</P>
<P>
   Dick aims gun at Jane.
</P>
<P>
   Run, Jane! Run!
</P>
<P>
   See Jane run.
</P>
<P>
   Hear bang. Gun is loud.
</P>
<P>
   Father hears. Mother hears. Spot hears.
</P>
<P>
   Jane is fast.
</P>
<P>
   Bullet is faster.
</P>
<P>
   Down goes Jane.
</P>
<P>
   ``Oh, no,'' says Father.
</P>
<P>
   ``Oh, no,'' says Mother.
</P>
<P>
   ``Bowwow,'' says Spot.
</P>
<P>
   Hear sirens.
</P>
<P>
   Sirens are loud.
</P>
<P>
   See lights.
</P>
<P>
   Lights are bright.
</P>
<P>
   Here come police. Here comes ambulance.
</P>
<P>
   There goes Jane.
</P>
<P>
   Weeeeeeeeeee.
</P>
<P>
   Go, Jane, go.
</P>
<P>
   Look, here come cameras.
</P>
<P>
   Look, here come reporters.
</P>
<P>
   ``Who?'' ask reporters.
</P>
<P>
   ``When?'' ask reporters.
</P>
<P>
   ``Why?'' ask reporters.
</P>
<P>
   See politicians. See politicians sigh. See politicians shrug.
</P>
<P>
   See children die.
</P>
<P>
   Look, there's Littleton, Colo. Look, there's Conyers, Ga. Look,
there's Paducah, Ky. Look, there's Springfield, Ore. Look, there's
Edinboro, Pa. Look, there's Pearl, Miss. Look, there's Flint, Mich.
</P>
<P>
   See the shooter. The shooter was 17. The shooter was 15. The
shooter was 13. The shooter was 11. The shooter was 6.
</P>
<P>
   See the victim. The victim was 18 and 17 and 16 and 15 and 14
and 13 and 12. The victim was 6.
</P>
<P>
   Look, there's Charlton Heston. He is Moses. He is the NRA.
</P>
<P>
   ``Whoa,'' says Charlton. ``See television? Television is bad.
See movies? Movies are bad. See magazines? Magazines are bad. See
guns. Guns are good.''
</P>
<P>
   Look, facts.
</P>
<P>
   Guns are No. 2 killer of young people. Guns increase risk of
homicide. Guns for self-defense are more likely to kill family
member or friend.
</P>
<P>
   See TV news. See rampage Wednesday in Pittsburgh. Seen enough?
</P>
<P>
   Look, there's Charlton again. Look, there are gun lobbyists.
Lobbyists are shiny. Lobbyists contribute cash.
</P>
<P>
   See politicians.
</P>
<P>
   See politicians take cash.
</P>
<P>
   See politicians run.
</P>
<P>
   Run, politicians, run.
</P>
<P>
   ``Bowwow,'' says Spot. &QL;
</P>
