<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-04 11:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6636 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      03-04 1802
